    [메모리 상태]

    변수명          | 값              | ID (주소)      | 타입
    --------------|-----------------|----------------|--------
    age           | {age:13} | {id(age):14} | int
    height        | {height:13} | {id(height):14} | float
    name          | "{name:10}" | {id(name):14} | str
    is_student    | {is_student:13} | {id(is_student):14} | bool
    """

    return visualization


